last_episode_to_air.name: Joou-sama wa M Dorei
last_episode_to_air.overview: Yumi (Yoshimi Terada) when she was little, her mother left her father, after that her father brought another woman home, she grew up as a girl who hates all men, she became a nurse in a big hospital, but that was not her main job, because her main job is to torture men.
